title: Content Court: TheQuartering
description: The court is BACK IN SESSION and this time the indictment is against Jeremy Hambly aka TheQuartering. Join us as we take a deep dive on the bumbling antics of one of the internet's biggest oafs on this edition of CONTENT COURT!
